## Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies or perspectives. The findings are limited to the context of the articles reviewed, which may not fully represent the diversity of organizational settings. Additionally, the search did not include primary research or interviews with industry professionals, which could provide further insights.

